<item>
            <title>[SPR-12152] ResponseBodyAdvice to accept null values?</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-12152</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ResponseBodyAdvice is amazing for my needs except for one thing, it doesn&apos;t seem to be triggered when the ResponseBody returns a null value.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is it possible to handle this case through the ResponseBodyAdvice?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="59610">SPR-12152</key>
            <summary>ResponseBodyAdvice to accept null values?</summary>
